Quick & easy filesharing over wifi

Stop using email to send files to people on your wifi. Any Send is copy & paste for your home or office network. Any Send works between devices. Send something from your Mac to your phone? No problem.

So simple its easy

  1. Copy a file.
  2. Paste it to someone.
  3. Done.
